Tent



We pitched the tent overlooking the Big Sur River. The river noise helped us sleep at night.
Taken Sunday, June 24, 2001, 03:57:26pm.  Original image size: 1600x1200, 1071kb
Technical details: Olympus C700UZ, 1/50s @ F2.8, ISO 100, 38mm
PS6 debloom, Curves 0:0 - 160:190 - 255:255, Unsharp Mask 2.0 70%
